content: **Join us on a cinematic adventure under the stars! Our midsummer movie event brings together the best in film and animation for a fun-filled family evening. With a stunning outdoor setting and nighttime screenings, get ready to be transported to another world. Don't miss out on this perfect summer experience, complete with a mix of modern and vintage movies, all set against a backdrop of vibrant, colorful summer hues.
